\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\cf0\b0\f1 As an abstraction, the scarcity of a resource in the game setting can be rated on the following scale (from least to most scarce):\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f2\'b7\tab\b\f1 Abundant:\b0  The resource is virtually everywhere; the average person probably has at least some of it at any given time.\par
\f2\'b7\tab\b\f1 Uncommon:\b0  The resource isn\rquote t something that you\rquote d just stumble upon accidentally but if you put concerted effort into it, you would probably find some.\par
\f2\'b7\tab\b\f1 Hard to Get:\b0  The resource is in short supply or is somehow heavily regulated; most people don\rquote t have ready access to it at all but if you have special access or know the right people, you can probably get some.\par
\f2\'b7\tab\b\f1 Very Hard to Get:\b0  The resource is absent from all the common places and even people with special access find it a significant challenge to track some down. Don\rquote t be surprised if you can\rquote t get any at all.\par
\f2\'b7\tab\b\f1 Impossible to Get:\b0  Stockpiles of this resource simply don\rquote t exist; people that are especially resourceful might have been prudent enough to snare some for their personal supply, but that\rquote s it.\par
