\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\cf0\b0\fs22 While the rules presented in this System Reference Document provide a fully-playable (if generic) tabletop roleplaying game, they are designed to also serve as the rules foundation for future games. Several resources are collected here which may assist with the design and definition of such games.\par
